# 统一换行：面向 Rocky 9.4 / Linux 部署，仓库内文本一律 LF，杜绝 CRLF 导致
# shell 脚本 "bad interpreter"、Dockerfile/entrypoint 失效等问题。
* text=auto eol=lf

# 明确按 LF 处理的文本类型
*.java   text eol=lf
*.kt     text eol=lf
*.xml    text eol=lf
*.yml    text eol=lf
*.yaml   text eol=lf
*.sql    text eol=lf
*.sh     text eol=lf
*.properties text eol=lf
*.json   text eol=lf
*.js     text eol=lf
*.ts     text eol=lf
*.vue    text eol=lf
*.css    text eol=lf
*.html   text eol=lf
*.md     text eol=lf
Dockerfile text eol=lf

# 二进制：不做换行/diff 处理
*.png    binary
*.jpg    binary
*.jpeg   binary
*.gif    binary
*.ico    binary
*.woff   binary
*.woff2  binary
*.ttf    binary
*.jar    binary
